#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""remctl-server — REST API for iCloud Reminders.

Exposes all remctl features as JSON endpoints over HTTP. Designed for
Tailscale-only access with Bearer token authentication.

Reads directly from the iCloud Reminders CoreData SQLite database.
Writes via AppleScript (update/complete/uncomplete/delete) for reliable
iCloud sync, with remctl-bridge (Swift EventKit) for creates and list
operations. Falls back to remctl CLI as a last resort.

Zero external dependencies — stdlib only.
"""

